snippet.title: Best VGM 863 - The Smurfs - The Mountains
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 706 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=13Uk8RB6kzQ

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
The Smurfs (1994)
The Mountains
Alberto Gonzalez
